---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout>
  <!-- HERO -->
  <section id="hero-section" class="relative -mt-18 md:-mt-20 hero-section-flex overflow-hidden" style="background-color: #001D52;">

    <!-- Neon gradient glow on the right side (aligned with globe at calc(50% - 50px)) -->
    <div class="absolute top-0 right-0 w-1/2 h-full pointer-events-none" style="background: radial-gradient(ellipse 40% 55% at 100% calc(50% - 50px), rgba(207,255,21,0.22) 0%, rgba(207,255,21,0.07) 35%, transparent 60%);"></div>

    <!-- Decorative rotating wireframe globe, peeking from the right edge of the section -->
    <canvas id="hero-globe" class="pointer-events-none absolute hidden lg:block" style="top: calc(50% - 50px); right: -280px; transform: translateY(-50%); width: 680px; height: 680px; z-index: 1; opacity: 0.95;"></canvas>

    <!-- Curved bottom edge -->
    <div class="absolute bottom-0 left-0 right-0 z-10 pointer-events-none" style="line-height: 0;">
      <svg viewBox="0 0 1440 200" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" preserveAspectRatio="none" class="w-full" style="height: 150px;">
        <path d="M0,0 Q720,200 1440,0 L1440,200 L0,200 Z" fill="#F9F6F0"/>
      </svg>
    </div>

    <!-- Hero Content -->
    <div class="relative z-10 w-full max-w-[1400px] mx-auto px-8 lg:px-16">
      <div class="hero-layout items-center">
        <!-- Left: Text -->
        <div id="hero-text">
          <h1 class="heading-serif text-4xl md:text-5xl lg:text-[3.8rem] text-white mb-8 leading-[1.1]">
            <span id="hero-title-line1" class="hero-text-split inline-block overflow-hidden">More business.</span><br />
            <span id="hero-title-line2" class="hero-text-split text-neon italic inline-block overflow-hidden">Less busyness.</span>
          </h1>
          <!-- Desktop: hardcoded line breaks -->
          <div id="hero-body" class="hero-fade-group" style="opacity: 0; transform: translateY(20px);">
          <div id="hero-para-desktop" class="text-white text-[15px] leading-[1.7]" style="white-space: pre-line;">Growing B2B teams don't have an ambition problem — they have
a friction problem. Bad data, manual outbound, busywork that
burns people out. Skief Labs builds the data and outbound
systems that fix that.</div>
          <!-- Mobile: natural flow (shown only on very small screens) -->
          <div id="hero-para-mobile" class="text-white text-sm leading-[1.7]" style="display: none;">
            <p>Growing B2B teams don't have an ambition problem — they have a friction problem. Bad data, manual outbound, busywork that burns people out. Skief Labs builds the data and outbound systems that fix that.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="mt-8 flex items-center gap-5 flex-wrap">
            <a href="/contact" class="btn-primary inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-xs !py-3.5 !px-6">
              Book a 30-minute discovery call
              <span class="btn-arrow">&rarr;</span>
            </a>
            <p class="text-white/50 text-sm italic">No pitch. No obligation. Just clarity.</p>
          </div>
          </div><!-- end hero-body -->
        </div>

        <!-- Right: Visual Flow Cards with SVG arrows overlay -->
        <div id="hero-cards" class="hero-cards-wrapper relative">

          <div class="hero-cards-inner relative" style="width: 550px; height: 490px; z-index: 2;">
            <!-- Card 1: Daily Friction -->
            <div class="hero-card hero-card-1 absolute rounded-[10px] px-6 py-4 text-center shadow-lg" style="width: 280px; height: 80px; top: 0; left: 30px; display: flex; flex-direction: column; justify-content: center; background-color: #F9F6F0;">
              <p class="font-serif text-2xl tracking-wide text-black/40"><s>Daily Friction</s></p>
              <p class="font-sans font-semibold text-xs mt-1 uppercase tracking-[0.08em] whitespace-nowrap text-black/60">Fragile &middot; Human-Dependent</p>
            </div>

            <!-- Card 2: Built Systems -->
            <div class="hero-card hero-card-2 absolute rounded-[10px] px-6 py-4 text-center shadow-lg" style="width: 280px; height: 80px; top: 195px; left: 250px; display: flex; flex-direction: column; justify-content: center; background-color: #CFFF15;">
              <div class="absolute -top-3 left-4 text-black text-[9px] font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.1em] rounded-[10px] text-center leading-none" style="padding: 4px 10px; background-color: #F9F6F0;">Transformation</div>
              <p class="font-serif text-black text-2xl tracking-wide">Built Systems</p>
              <p class="font-sans font-semibold text-xs mt-1 uppercase tracking-[0.08em] text-black/60">Data &middot; Outbound</p>
            </div>

            <!-- Card 3: Business Forward -->
            <div class="hero-card hero-card-3 absolute rounded-[10px] px-6 py-4 text-center shadow-lg" style="width: 280px; height: 80px; top: 390px; left: 60px; display: flex; flex-direction: column; justify-content: center; background-color: #F9F6F0;">
              <p class="font-serif text-black text-2xl tracking-wide whitespace-nowrap">Business Forward</p>
              <p class="font-sans font-semibold text-xs mt-1 uppercase tracking-[0.08em] text-black/60">Focused &middot; Scalable</p>
            </div>

            <!-- SVG Arrows connecting the cards -->
            <svg class="absolute inset-0 pointer-events-none" width="550" height="490" viewBox="0 0 550 490" fill="none" style="z-index: 1;">
              <g class="hero-arrow hero-arrow-1">
                <path d="M 190 92 L 190 132 L 410 132 L 410 175" stroke="#F9F6F0" stroke-width="1.5" fill="none" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" pathLength="1"/>
                <polygon points="405,173 410,185 415,173" fill="#F9F6F0"/>
              </g>

              <g class="hero-arrow hero-arrow-2">
                <path d="M 370 287 L 370 330 L 200 330 L 200 370" stroke="#F9F6F0" stroke-width="1.5" fill="none" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" pathLength="1"/>
                <polygon points="195,368 200,380 205,368" fill="#F9F6F0"/>
              </g>
            </svg>
          </div>

        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- THE PROBLEM -->
  <section id="problem-section" class="bg-linen py-24 md:py-32 reveal">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6 lg:px-8 text-center">
      <!-- Section Label -->
      <div class="inline-block border border-red-400 text-red-500 text-[10px] uppercase tracking-[0.2em] font-semibold px-4 py-1.5 rounded mb-8">
        The Problem
      </div>

      <h2 class="font-serif text-2xl md:text-3xl lg:text-[2.2rem] text-navy mb-12 leading-[1.25] tracking-[-0.02em] max-w-3xl mx-auto">
        Your team is doing work the<br /><em class="italic">business should be doing for them.</em>
      </h2>

      <!-- Content Card -->
      <div class="bg-linen border-2 border-navy rounded-[10px] p-8 md:p-10 text-left shadow-[6px_6px_0px_0px_#001D52]">
        <div class="space-y-4 text-black/80 text-base leading-relaxed">
          <p>As B2B companies grow, tools multiply, data fragments, and your best people become the glue — manually researching, chasing, reconciling.</p>
          <p>The cost is real: slower decisions, inconsistent outbound, senior time absorbed by work that shouldn't require senior people.</p>
          <p class="text-black font-bold">
            Adding more software doesn't fix this. Adding more people only delays it.
          </p>
          <p>What changes things is replacing fragile, human-dependent effort with systems that work quietly in the background.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- WHAT WE DO -->
  <section class="bg-linen py-24 md:py-32 reveal">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto text-center mb-16">
        <h2 class="font-serif text-2xl md:text-3xl lg:text-[2.2rem] text-navy mb-4 leading-[1.25] tracking-[-0.02em]">
          Two problems. Solved seriously.
        </h2>
        <p class="text-black text-base md:text-lg leading-relaxed">We work on two specific things. We don't do general automation.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 lg:gap-10 reveal">
        <!-- Data Intelligence -->
        <a href="/services#data-intelligence" class="service-card group bg-linen rounded-[10px] p-6 md:p-8 border-2">
          <!-- Visual Box -->
          <div class="rounded-[10px] mb-6 flex items-center justify-center overflow-hidden" style="background-color: #D9D9D9; aspect-ratio: 16/9;">
            <svg viewBox="0 0 400 220" class="w-[94%] h-auto" fill="none">
              <!-- 3 Dashed connector lines (from doc right edge to center box left edge) -->
              <line x1="90" y1="43"  x2="160" y2="110" stroke="#0A60FF" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-dasharray="4 4"/>
              <line x1="90" y1="110" x2="160" y2="110" stroke="#0A60FF" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-dasharray="4 4"/>
              <line x1="90" y1="177" x2="160" y2="110" stroke="#0A60FF" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-dasharray="4 4"/>

              <!-- Traveling navy dots (randomized delays + varied durations so they drift, no marching sequence) -->
              <circle class="di-dot" cx="90" cy="43"  r="5" fill="#001D52" style="--tx: 70px; --ty: 67px;  animation-delay: 0.2s; animation-duration: 2.7s;"/>
              <circle class="di-dot" cx="90" cy="110" r="5" fill="#001D52" style="--tx: 70px; --ty: 0px;   animation-delay: 1.6s; animation-duration: 3.3s;"/>
              <circle class="di-dot" cx="90" cy="177" r="5" fill="#001D52" style="--tx: 70px; --ty: -67px; animation-delay: 0.7s; animation-duration: 2.4s;"/>

              <!-- 3 Document boxes (opaque fill so they overlap the dot's left half at the starting edge) -->
              <rect x="15" y="25" width="75" height="36" rx="4" fill="#D9D9D9" stroke="#0A60FF" stroke-width="2"/>
              <line x1="25" y1="35" x2="80" y2="35" stroke="#0A60FF" stroke-width="1.5"/>
              <line x1="25" y1="43" x2="75" y2="43" stroke="#0A60FF" stroke-width="1.5"/>
              <line x1="25" y1="51" x2="65" y2="51" stroke="#0A60FF" stroke-width="1.5"/>

              <rect x="15" y="92" width="75" height="36" rx="4" fill="#D9D9D9" stroke="#0A60FF" stroke-width="2"/>
              <line x1="25" y1="102" x2="80" y2="102" stroke="#0A60FF" stroke-width="1.5"/>
              <line x1="25" y1="110" x2="75" y2="110" stroke="#0A60FF" stroke-width="1.5"/>
              <line x1="25" y1="118" x2="65" y2="118" stroke="#0A60FF" stroke-width="1.5"/>

              <rect x="15" y="159" width="75" height="36" rx="4" fill="#D9D9D9" stroke="#0A60FF" stroke-width="2"/>
              <line x1="25" y1="169" x2="80" y2="169" stroke="#0A60FF" stroke-width="1.5"/>
              <line x1="25" y1="177" x2="75" y2="177" stroke="#0A60FF" stroke-width="1.5"/>
              <line x1="25" y1="185" x2="65" y2="185" stroke="#0A60FF" stroke-width="1.5"/>

              <!-- Central processor box (landscape rectangle, opaque fill so it overlaps lines/dots behind it) -->
              <rect x="160" y="78" width="100" height="64" rx="8" fill="#D9D9D9" stroke="#0A60FF" stroke-width="2"/>

              <!-- Outer circle ring inside the box -->
              <circle cx="210" cy="110" r="22" fill="none" stroke="#0A60FF" stroke-width="1.5"/>

              <!-- 8 short rays from outer ring outward -->
              <g stroke="#0A60FF" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round">
                <line x1="210" y1="88"  x2="210" y2="83"/>
                <line x1="210" y1="132" x2="210" y2="137"/>
                <line x1="188" y1="110" x2="183" y2="110"/>
                <line x1="232" y1="110" x2="237" y2="110"/>
                <line x1="194" y1="94"  x2="191" y2="91"/>
                <line x1="226" y1="94"  x2="229" y2="91"/>
                <line x1="194" y1="126" x2="191" y2="129"/>
                <line x1="226" y1="126" x2="229" y2="129"/>
              </g>

              <!-- Inner filled circle -->
              <circle cx="210" cy="110" r="10" fill="#0A60FF"/>

              <!-- Animated pulse ring (open-close) -->
              <circle class="di-pulse" cx="210" cy="110" r="10" fill="none" stroke="#0A60FF" stroke-width="2"/>

              <!-- Long arrow from center box to chart box -->
              <line x1="260" y1="110" x2="297" y2="110" stroke="#0A60FF" stroke-width="2"/>
              <polygon points="295,105 305,110 295,115" fill="#0A60FF"/>

              <!-- Chart container (landscape rectangle, opaque so it overlaps the arrow tail) -->
              <rect x="305" y="78" width="85" height="64" rx="8" fill="#D9D9D9" stroke="#0A60FF" stroke-width="2"/>

              <!-- Bars inside chart (5 ascending) -->
              <rect x="314" y="122" width="10" height="16" fill="#0A60FF"/>
              <rect x="329" y="112" width="10" height="26" fill="#0A60FF"/>
              <rect x="344" y="100" width="10" height="38" fill="#0A60FF"/>
              <rect x="359" y="88"  width="10" height="50" fill="#0A60FF"/>
              <rect x="374" y="82"  width="10" height="56" fill="#0A60FF"/>
            </svg>
          </div>

          <h3 class="font-serif text-xl md:text-2xl text-navy tracking-[-0.01em] mb-3">Data Intelligence</h3>
          <p class="text-black/80 text-base leading-relaxed mb-6">
            The research, enrichment, and data pipelines your team currently does by hand — built as automated systems.
          </p>

          <div class="flex items-center justify-between pt-6 border-t border-navy/20">
            <span class="service-card-cta subhead-condensed text-xs text-black tracking-[0.2em] transition-colors duration-200">Explore Systems</span>
            <span class="service-card-arrow" aria-hidden="true">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
                <line x1="7" y1="17" x2="17" y2="7"/>
                <polyline points="7 7 17 7 17 17"/>
              </svg>
            </span>
          </div>
        </a>

        <!-- Sales Acceleration -->
        <a href="/services#sales-acceleration" class="service-card group bg-linen rounded-[10px] p-6 md:p-8 border-2">
          <!-- Visual Box -->
          <div class="rounded-[10px] mb-6 flex items-center justify-center overflow-hidden" style="background-color: #D9D9D9; aspect-ratio: 16/9;">
            <svg viewBox="0 0 400 220" class="w-[92%] h-auto" fill="none">
              <!-- Dashed connectors from email box edges to 6 outer nodes -->
              <line x1="170" y1="95"  x2="80"  y2="42"  stroke="#0A60FF" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-dasharray="4 4"/>
              <line x1="230" y1="95"  x2="320" y2="42"  stroke="#0A60FF" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-dasharray="4 4"/>
              <line x1="170" y1="110" x2="45"  y2="110" stroke="#0A60FF" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-dasharray="4 4"/>
              <line x1="230" y1="110" x2="355" y2="110" stroke="#0A60FF" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-dasharray="4 4"/>
              <line x1="170" y1="125" x2="80"  y2="178" stroke="#0A60FF" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-dasharray="4 4"/>
              <line x1="230" y1="125" x2="320" y2="178" stroke="#0A60FF" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-dasharray="4 4"/>

              <!-- Traveling navy dots (randomized delays + varied durations so they drift, no marching sequence) -->
              <circle class="sa-dot" cx="170" cy="95"  r="5" fill="#001D52" style="--tx: -90px;  --ty: -53px; animation-delay: 0s;   animation-duration: 3s;"/>
              <circle class="sa-dot" cx="230" cy="95"  r="5" fill="#001D52" style="--tx:  90px;  --ty: -53px; animation-delay: 1.4s; animation-duration: 2.7s;"/>
              <circle class="sa-dot" cx="170" cy="110" r="5" fill="#001D52" style="--tx: -125px; --ty: 0px;   animation-delay: 0.6s; animation-duration: 3.4s;"/>
              <circle class="sa-dot" cx="230" cy="110" r="5" fill="#001D52" style="--tx:  125px; --ty: 0px;   animation-delay: 2.1s; animation-duration: 2.8s;"/>
              <circle class="sa-dot" cx="170" cy="125" r="5" fill="#001D52" style="--tx: -90px;  --ty: 53px;  animation-delay: 1.0s; animation-duration: 3.2s;"/>
              <circle class="sa-dot" cx="230" cy="125" r="5" fill="#001D52" style="--tx:  90px;  --ty: 53px;  animation-delay: 0.3s; animation-duration: 2.5s;"/>

              <!-- 6 Outer nodes (opaque fill so dots arriving get overlapped by the ring) -->
              <circle cx="80"  cy="42"  r="10" fill="#D9D9D9" stroke="#0A60FF" stroke-width="2"/>
              <circle cx="80"  cy="42"  r="4"  fill="#0A60FF"/>
              <circle cx="320" cy="42"  r="10" fill="#D9D9D9" stroke="#0A60FF" stroke-width="2"/>
              <circle cx="320" cy="42"  r="4"  fill="#0A60FF"/>
              <circle cx="45"  cy="110" r="10" fill="#D9D9D9" stroke="#0A60FF" stroke-width="2"/>
              <circle cx="45"  cy="110" r="4"  fill="#0A60FF"/>
              <circle cx="355" cy="110" r="10" fill="#D9D9D9" stroke="#0A60FF" stroke-width="2"/>
              <circle cx="355" cy="110" r="4"  fill="#0A60FF"/>
              <circle cx="80"  cy="178" r="10" fill="#D9D9D9" stroke="#0A60FF" stroke-width="2"/>
              <circle cx="80"  cy="178" r="4"  fill="#0A60FF"/>
              <circle cx="320" cy="178" r="10" fill="#D9D9D9" stroke="#0A60FF" stroke-width="2"/>
              <circle cx="320" cy="178" r="4"  fill="#0A60FF"/>

              <!-- Central email box (opaque, drawn on top so dots emerging from its edges stay hidden inside) -->
              <rect x="170" y="85" width="60" height="50" rx="8" fill="#0A60FF"/>
              <rect x="182" y="100" width="36" height="22" rx="2" fill="none" stroke="#FFFFFF" stroke-width="2"/>
              <path d="M 182 102 L 200 118 L 218 102" stroke="#FFFFFF" stroke-width="2" fill="none" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
            </svg>
          </div>

          <h3 class="font-serif text-xl md:text-2xl text-navy tracking-[-0.01em] mb-3">Sales Acceleration</h3>
          <p class="text-black/80 text-base leading-relaxed mb-6">
            The outbound system your team should already have — designed, built, and operated by us.
          </p>

          <div class="flex items-center justify-between pt-6 border-t border-navy/20">
            <span class="service-card-cta subhead-condensed text-xs text-black tracking-[0.2em] transition-colors duration-200">Explore Systems</span>
            <span class="service-card-arrow" aria-hidden="true">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
                <line x1="7" y1="17" x2="17" y2="7"/>
                <polyline points="7 7 17 7 17 17"/>
              </svg>
            </span>
          </div>
        </a>
      </div>

      <!-- A note on AI & Automation -->
      <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto mt-16 bg-linen rounded-[10px] p-8 text-center border-2 border-navy shadow-[6px_6px_0px_0px_#001D52]">
        <p class="font-serif text-black text-lg mb-3"><span class="bg-neon px-2 py-0.5">A note on AI &amp; Automation</span></p>
        <p class="text-black/70 text-sm leading-relaxed" style="white-space: pre-line;">You'll notice we don't list AI and automation as a service. That's intentional. AI and automation
are how we build — not what we sell. The technology is never the point. The point is the outcome.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- WHO THIS IS FOR -->
  <section class="bg-linen py-24 md:py-32 reveal">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12 lg:gap-16 items-center">
        <div>
          <h2 class="font-serif text-2xl md:text-3xl lg:text-[2.2rem] text-navy mb-6 leading-[1.25] tracking-[-0.02em]">
            This works best for a specific kind of company.
          </h2>
          <p class="text-black text-base md:text-lg leading-relaxed mb-8">
            B2B teams — typically 10 to 200 people — where:
          </p>
          <ul class="space-y-4 text-black text-base md:text-lg leading-relaxed mb-8 reveal reveal-children">
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <span class="inline-flex items-center justify-center w-5 h-5 bg-neon rounded text-navy text-xs flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5">&#10003;</span>
              <span>Growth has outpaced the systems underneath it</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <span class="inline-flex items-center justify-center w-5 h-5 bg-neon rounded text-navy text-xs flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5">&#10003;</span>
              <span>Manual effort increases faster than headcount</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <span class="inline-flex items-center justify-center w-5 h-5 bg-neon rounded text-navy text-xs flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5">&#10003;</span>
              <span>Data lives in spreadsheets, inboxes, and people's heads</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <span class="inline-flex items-center justify-center w-5 h-5 bg-neon rounded text-navy text-xs flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5">&#10003;</span>
              <span>Leadership wants outcomes, not another tool to manage</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <span class="inline-flex items-center justify-center w-5 h-5 bg-neon rounded text-navy text-xs flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5">&#10003;</span>
              <span>There is no internal automation or RevOps function — by choice or reality</span>
            </li>
          </ul>
          <p class="text-black/70 text-base">
            If your people are the glue holding your data or outbound together, that's the pattern we fix.
          </p>
        </div>
        <!-- Image with neon accent shadow -->
        <div class="relative max-w-sm mx-auto lg:mx-0 lg:ml-auto w-full">
          <img src="/images/sk2.jpg" alt="Team collaboration" class="w-full rounded-[10px] object-cover shadow-[8px_8px_0px_0px_#CFFF15]" style="aspect-ratio: 4/5;" />
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- WHY SKIEF LABS -->
  <section class="bg-linen py-16 md:py-20 reveal">
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-6 lg:px-8">
      <!-- Header -->
      <div class="text-center mb-10">
        <h2 class="font-serif text-2xl md:text-3xl lg:text-[2.2rem] text-navy mb-4 leading-[1.25] tracking-[-0.02em]">
          Why choose <span class="italic">Skief Labs</span>?
        </h2>
        <p class="text-black text-base md:text-lg leading-relaxed max-w-2xl mx-auto mb-1">
          We are not an agency. Not a consultancy. Not a tool vendor.
        </p>
        <p class="text-black text-base md:text-lg leading-relaxed mx-auto"><span class="neon-underline">We're a small firm that builds systems — and operates them when that's what the work requires.</span></p>
      </div>

      <!-- All 4 cards in one grid -->
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-5 reveal">
        <!-- Senior-Led -->
        <div class="why-card bg-linen rounded-[10px] p-6 border-2 text-center">
          <div class="mb-4 flex h-12 w-12 items-center justify-center rounded-[10px] bg-linen mx-auto">
            <svg class="h-6 w-6" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#000000" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
              <path d="M16 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-4-4H6a4 4 0 0 0-4 4v2"/>
